 clang/include/clang/Driver/Options.td         |  9 ++--
 clang/lib/Driver/ToolChains/Gnu.cpp           | 22 ++++++++++
 clang/test/Driver/gcc-install-dir.cpp         | 43 +++++++++++++++++++
